Three tiers: 
1. The DigitalOcean approach: non-financial incentives such as Kindles
2. The 3M approach: financial/ non-financial incentives that are tied directly to a company initative (Energy Efficiency) 
3. The PepsiCo approach: 40% of an associates annual bonus is tied to how they've helped others

https://www.forbes.com/sites/lisabodell/2019/11/30/reward-programs-that-actually-boost-collaboration/?sh=2124cbfe71ee
